Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-EIC Major Revision in variants involving major revision cycles

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the first occurrence of any reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Initial Reviewer Selection)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Average time it takes the review process to progress from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to the first AE-involved activity (e.g., SW-Awaiting AE Assignment or SW-Initial Reviewer Selection)

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in cases that eventually lead to acceptance versus rejection
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and activity SW-EIC Accept for cases where activity SW-EIC Accept occurs

Name: Time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to the final decision activity (e.g., SW-EIC Accept, SW-EIC Reject, or SW-EIC Major Revision) grouped by variant type
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'
